OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1773947498
OL,3,CQueue to get meningitis B vaccine at
OL,4,CKent University closed 'due to
OL,5,Ccapacity'
OL,7,FThe queue to get a meningitis B
OL,8,Fvaccine at the University of Kent's
OL,9,FCanterbury campus has closed "due to
OL,10,Fcapacity".
OL,12,FIn a Facebook post on Thursday
OL,13,Fafternoon, the university said: "The
OL,14,Fqueue has been closed as nursing staff
OL,15,Fare unable to see any more people
OL,16,Fwithin the clinic's remaining opening
OL,17,Fhours today.
OL,19,F"The team have been working incredibly
OL,20,Fhard to vaccinate as many people as
OL,21,Fpossible."
OL,26,@qD@^OUrD@IO]uD@aOU{D@AOU}D@JO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/7
