PN,41302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1773947498
OL,3,CQueue to get meningitis B vaccine at
OL,4,CKent University closed 'due to
OL,5,Ccapacity'
OL,7,FThe university said the vaccination
OL,8,Fclinic will reopen on Friday from 9am
OL,9,Fto 5pm, and advised for people to be
OL,10,Fin the queue by 2pm.
OL,12,FIt's understood medics wanted to
OL,13,Fvaccinate the final person at 4.30pm,
OL,14,Fin order to give them time to sit and
OL,15,Fwait for 15 minutes afterwards ` as
OL,16,Fevery person who has received the jab
OL,17,Fhas had to do.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/7
