PN,41303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1773947498
OL,3,CQueue to get meningitis B vaccine at
OL,4,CKent University closed 'due to
OL,5,Ccapacity'
OL,7,FA student who went to the nightclub at
OL,8,Fthe centre of the meningitis outbreak
OL,9,Fwas one of those turned away from the
OL,10,Fvaccine queue.
OL,12,FHayden Taylor, 19, a radiography
OL,13,Fstudent at Canterbury Christ Church,
OL,14,Fwent to the Club Chemistry nightclub
OL,15,Fon 12 March.
OL,17,FHe was turned away by security staff
OL,18,Fwhen he arrived at the centre at
OL,19,Faround 3pm on Thursday.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
