OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,414,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1773947498
OL,3,CQueue to get meningitis B vaccine at
OL,4,CKent University closed 'due to
OL,5,Ccapacity'
OL,7,F"I had the antibiotics already," Mr
OL,8,FTaylor said.
OL,10,F"We already knew it was going to be
OL,11,Fbusy."
OL,13,FIsobel, 21, an English literature
OL,14,Fstudent at the University of Kent, was
OL,15,Fturned away after a 80-minute drive to
OL,16,Fthe centre by her mother.
OL,26,@oD@AOUoD@`O]rD@AOUsD@FO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/7
