PN,41305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1773947498
OL,3,CQueue to get meningitis B vaccine at
OL,4,CKent University closed 'due to
OL,5,Ccapacity'
OL,7,FSpeaking outside the vaccine centre,
OL,8,FIsobel, who chose not to give her
OL,9,Fsurname, said: "My mum has had to
OL,10,Fdrive me an hour and 20 minutes to get
OL,11,Fthe vaccine.
OL,13,F"It is very inconvenient.
OL,15,F"I'm coming back tomorrow and hope
OL,16,Fthat they have got some."
OL,18,FIt comes as the Health Secretary urged
OL,19,Fmore people to get antibiotics or the
OL,20,Fvaccine for meningitis during a visit
OL,21,Fto the vaccination centre on Thursday.
OL,26,@qD@POUuD@AOUxD@YO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/7
