PN,41306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1773947498
OL,3,CQueue to get meningitis B vaccine at
OL,4,CKent University closed 'due to
OL,5,Ccapacity'
OL,7,FWes Streeting said anyone who visited
OL,8,FChemistry nightclub in the city from 5
OL,9,FMarch onwards should get antibiotics
OL,10,Fand the vaccine.
OL,12,FThe University of Kent said 600
OL,13,Fmeningitis B (menB) vaccines had been
OL,14,Fadministered on Wednesday, after
OL,15,Fhundreds of students joined a queue
OL,16,Foutside the campus sports centre.
OL,18,FIt's not yet known how many people
OL,19,Fhave received the jab on Thursday.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/7
